  • Classes in agents used by agents
    Class Description
    BikeAgent
    The main aim of Bike agent is to get from point A to point B.
    BusAgent
    The main aim of Bus agent if to circulate between point A and B and stop at bus stops in order to gather all Traveler agents.
    BusManagerAgent
    The class handles communication with bus agent and pedestrian agent in case of trouble on the road
    CarAgent
    The main aim of Car agent is to get from point A to B.
    IdGenerator
    Generates ID for agents
    LightManagerAgent
    The main aim of LightManager agent is to manage a specific group of lights and control traffic.
    PedestrianAgent
    The number of PedestrianAgent agents in the system is configurable from the GUI.
    StationAgent
    StationManager agent represents a bus stop.
